 Replacement","href":"/zh/others/nvbit-tutorial/tools/mov_replace/","depth":3},{"title":"NVBit Tutorial: Opcode Histogram","href":"/zh/others/nvbit-tutorial/tools/opcode_hist/","depth":3},{"title":"NVBit Tutorial Tools","href":"/zh/others/nvbit-tutorial/tools/","depth":2},{"title":"NVBit Tutorial: Register Value Recording","href":"/zh/others/nvbit-tutorial/tools/record_reg_vals/","depth":3},{"title":"hXDP: Efficient Software Packet Processing on FPGA NICs","href":"/zh/others/papers/osdi20-brunella/","depth":2},{"title":"论文与研究","href":"/zh/others/papers/","depth":1},{"title":"ebpf usecases analysis","href":"/zh/others/usecases/","depth":1}]}]}},"__N_SSG":true}